      'Built a CMS-driven events calendar directly in Framer, giving the marketing team full autonomy to add, edit, and remove events without touching code',
      'Designed responsive layouts that used full-bleed photography with dimensional callouts (ceiling height, floor area, parking capacity) to communicate physical scale',
      'Implemented scroll-based animations and interactive section reveals in Framer to give the site the premium, editorial feel expected of a venue at this tier',
